{"tid":1503771,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"825 真 。Be Water","createTime":"2019-08-25T05:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T05:44:38.000Z","uid":69845,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3504a56cc3a243bcc48f6abddd29648ed78536a","tid":1503771,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"經過琴日牛頭角一役<br />\n<br />\n今日荃葵青重新熟習番<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Be Water</span>please<br />\n<br />\n等班狗地出黎 跟住鬥跑 有點唔明智<br />\n<br />\nRoad block 平放 等佢地唔易跑 甚至行都難<br />\n<br />\n再堅d真係唔走 鬥片 但時間一長 佢地有槍 唔夠做 <br />\n<br />\n佢地無封大窩口 我估因為近新界南總部<br />\n<br />\n小心被埋伏 個人認為葵興比較安全d<br />\n<br />\n利申： 葵芳讀書 住荃葵青 5/8 荃灣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">黑 警 死 全 家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後 一定現場決定 只想計劃多少少</span><br />\n<br />\n一陣見"},{"pid":"d548e606329c0fa63f1c4277184729ebbebc4dc4","tid":1503771,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"825"},{"pid":"87d17767f2381a5646dcf808a56648539b19ec9f","tid":1503771,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"825"},{"pid":"403822b91415d7ddf0401720361d0ac58d724959","tid":1503771,"uid":69845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"825"},{"pid":"b9b17757056c814420223a7c0177b2e20a5b19db","tid":1503771,"uid":110509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span>